| Reset Password | `04-reset-password.html` | New password, Confirm password, Password strength indicator |
| Sign Up Page | `05-signup.html` | Email, Password, Full Name, Phone (optional), Profile photo (optional), Location (optional), User type selector (Attendee/Organizer) |

