## Design System & Components

### Color Palette

#### Primary Colors
```css
Primary Blue:     #3B82F6  (rgb(59, 130, 246))
Primary Dark:     #2563EB  (rgb(37, 99, 235))
Primary Light:    #EFF6FF  (rgb(239, 246, 255))
Secondary:        #1D4ED8  (rgb(29, 78, 216))
Purple Accent:    #8B5CF6  (rgb(139, 92, 246))
```

#### Neutral Colors
```css
Dark:             #1E293B  (Slate 800)
Gray 900:         #0F172A
Gray 800:         #1E293B
Gray 700:         #334155
Gray 600:         #475569
Gray 500:         #64748B
Gray 400:         #94A3B8
Gray 300:         #CBD5E1
Gray 200:         #E2E8F0
Gray 100:         #F1F5F9
Gray 50:          #F8FAFC
```

#### Utility Colors
```css
Success Green:    #10B981
Warning Yellow:   #F59E0B
Error Red:        #EF4444
Info Blue:        #3B82F6
```

### Typography

#### Font Family
```css
Primary Font: 'Inter', sans-serif
Fallback: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif
```

**Loading:**
```html
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
```

#### Font Sizes
| Element | Size | Weight | Usage |
|---------|------|--------|-------|
| Page Titles | 36px (text-4xl) | 600 (Semibold) | Dashboard headings |
| Section Headers | 24px (text-2xl) | 600 (Semibold) | Section titles |
| Card Titles | 18px (text-lg) | 600 (Semibold) | Event cards, modals |
| Body Text | 16px (text-base) | 400 (Regular) | Descriptions, content |
| Small Text | 14px (text-sm) | 400-500 | Labels, captions |
| Tiny Text | 12px (text-xs) | 400 | Helper text, timestamps |

### Spacing System

**Tailwind Spacing Scale:**
```
4px   = 1  (space-1, p-1, m-1)
8px   = 2  (space-2, p-2, m-2)
12px  = 3  (space-3, p-3, m-3)
16px  = 4  (space-4, p-4, m-4)
20px  = 5  (space-5, p-5, m-5)
24px  = 6  (space-6, p-6, m-6)
32px  = 8  (space-8, p-8, m-8)
48px  = 12 (space-12, p-12, m-12)
```

**Common Patterns:**
- Card padding: `p-6` (24px)
- Button padding: `px-5 py-2.5` (20px horizontal, 10px vertical)
- Section spacing: `mb-8` or `mb-12` (32px or 48px)
- Input height: `h-11` (44px)

### Component Library

#### 1. Buttons

##### Primary Button
```html
<button class="bg-primary hover:bg-blue-600 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium flex items-center gap-2 shadow-sm transition-all">
  Button Text
</button>
```

##### Secondary Button
```html
<button class="bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 text-gray-700 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium border border-gray-200 shadow-sm transition-all">
  Button Text
</button>
```

##### Destructive Button
```html
<button class="bg-red-500 hover:bg-red-600 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium shadow-sm transition-all">
  Delete
</button>
```

##### Icon Button
```html
<button class="p-2 text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg transition-colors">
  <span class="iconify" data-icon="lucide:more-horizontal" data-width="20"></span>
</button>
```

#### 2. Form Inputs

##### Text Input
```html
<input type="text"
  class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg text-sm text-gray-900 placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary transition-all"
  placeholder="Enter text...">
```

##### Search Input
```html
<div class="relative">
  <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3.5 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
    <span class="iconify text-gray-400" data-icon="lucide:search" data-width="18"></span>
  </div>
  <input type="text"
    class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg text-sm focus:outline-none focus:bg-white focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary"
    placeholder="Search...">
</div>
```

##### Select Dropdown
```html
<select class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg text-sm text-gray-900 focus:outline-none focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary">
  <option>Option 1</option>
  <option>Option 2</option>
</select>
```

##### Textarea
```html
<textarea rows="4"
  class="w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg text-sm text-gray-900 placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary resize-none"
  placeholder="Enter description..."></textarea>
```

#### 3. Cards

##### Event Card
```html
