<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Pending</span>
<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-red-100 text-red-800 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Cancelled</span>
<span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Draft</span>

<!-- Category Tags -->
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg">Music</span>
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-50 text-purple-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg">Arts</span>
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-50 text-orange-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg">Food</span>
```

#### 8. Empty States

```html
<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-12 px-4 text-center">
  <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
    <span class="iconify text-gray-400" data-icon="lucide:calendar-x" data-width="32"></span>
  </div>
  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">No events found</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6 max-w-sm">You haven't created any events yet. Get started by creating your first event.</p>
  <button class="bg-primary text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium">
    Create Event
  </button>
</div>
```

