## User Flow Diagrams

### Attendee User Flow

```
[Splash Screen]
    ↓
[Login / Sign Up] ←→ [Forgot Password] → [Reset Password]
    ↓
[Home Page]
    ├── Featured Events → [Event Detail] → [Checkout] → [Order Confirmation]
    ├── Categories → [Filtered Events] → [Event Detail]
    ├── Upcoming Events → [Event Detail]
    └── Events Near You → [Event Detail]

[Search Tab]
    └── Search Results → [Event Detail]

[My Tickets Tab]
    ├── Upcoming Tickets → [Ticket Detail] → [Ticket Transfer]
    └── Past Tickets → [Review Submission]

[Profile Tab]
    ├── Wishlist → [Event Detail]
    ├── Edit Profile
    ├── Settings
    │   ├── Notifications
    │   ├── Payment Methods
    │   ├── Privacy
    │   └── Help
    └── Logout → [Login]
```

### Organizer User Flow

```
[Splash Screen]
    ↓
[Login / Sign Up]
    ↓
[Dashboard]
    ├── Stats Overview
    ├── Recent Sales
    └── Upcoming Events → [Event Management]

[Events Tab]
    ├── Active Events → [Event Management]
    │                      ├── Edit → [Event Creation (Edit Mode)]
    │                      ├── View Attendees → [Attendee List]
    │                      ├── Send Update
    │                      └── Cancel Event
    ├── Past Events → [Event Management (Read-only)]
    ├── Draft Events → [Event Creation (Continue)]
    └── [Create Event] → [Event Creation] (5 steps)
                            ├── Step 1: Basic Info
                            ├── Step 2: Date & Location
                            ├── Step 3: Media
                            ├── Step 4: Tickets
                            └── Step 5: Review & Publish → [Event Management]

[Attendee List]
    ├── Search Attendees
    ├── Check-in Toggle
    └── Export to CSV

[Profile Tab]
    ├── Profile Header
    ├── Reviews
    └── Settings
        ├── Payout Settings
        ├── Notifications
        ├── Help
        └── Logout → [Login]
```

### Admin User Flow

```
[Admin Splash]
    ↓
[Login]
    ↓
[Admin Dashboard]
    ├── Statistics Cards (Users, Events, Revenue, Sales)
    ├── Period Filter
    ├── Charts
    └── Recent Activity

[Attendees Management]
    ├── List All Attendees
    ├── Search & Filter
    ├── Create New Attendee
    ├── Edit Attendee
    └── Suspend Attendee

[Organizers Management]
    ├── List All Organizers
    ├── Search & Filter
    ├── Create New Organizer
    ├── Edit Organizer
    ├── Verify Organizer
    └── Suspend Organizer

[Events Management]
    ├── List All Events
    ├── Filter by Status/Date/Category
    ├── View Event Details
    ├── Cancel Event
    └── Feature Event

[Transactions Management]
    ├── List All Transactions
    ├── Search & Filter
    └── Process Refund

[Reviews Management]
    ├── List All Reviews
    ├── Search & Filter
    ├── Hide Review
    ├── Publish Review
    └── Delete Review

[Export Data]
    ├── Export Users (CSV/Excel)
    ├── Export Events (CSV/Excel)
    ├── Export Transactions (CSV/Excel)
    └── Export Reviews (CSV/Excel)
```

