### Attendee Pages

#### 5. Home Page (`06-home.html`)

**Purpose:** Main event discovery page

**Layout Structure:**
1. **Top Navigation Bar** (Sticky, 72px height)
   - Logo (left)
   - Search bar (center, max 480px)
   - Location button + Profile avatar (right)

2. **Hero Section** (400px height)
   - Background image with overlay
   - Headline text
   - CTA button

3. **Featured Events Section**
   - Horizontal scrollable carousel
   - Event cards: Image, Title, Date, Venue, Price
   - Click → Event Detail Page

4. **Categories Section**
   - Grid layout (responsive: 2 cols mobile, 4 cols tablet, 6 cols desktop)
   - Category chips with icons
   - Click → Filter events by category

5. **Upcoming Events Section**
   - Vertical list of event cards
   - Infinite scroll pagination
   - Each card: Image, Title, Date, Venue, Price, Attendee count

6. **Events Near You Section**
   - Location-based recommendations
   - Shows distance from user location
   - Uses geolocation API

**Bottom Navigation** (Mobile only, 64px height)
- Home, Search, My Tickets, Profile tabs

**Implementation Notes:**
```javascript
// Infinite scroll
const [events, setEvents] = useState([]);
const [page, setPage] = useState(1);
const [hasMore, setHasMore] = useState(true);

const loadMoreEvents = async () => {
  const newEvents = await fetchEvents(page);
  setEvents([...events, ...newEvents]);
  setPage(page + 1);
  if (newEvents.length === 0) setHasMore(false);
};

// Intersection Observer for infinite scroll
useEffect(() => {
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    if (entries[0].isIntersecting && hasMore) {
      loadMoreEvents();
    }
  });
  observer.observe(lastEventRef.current);
  return () => observer.disconnect();
}, [hasMore]);
```

**Featured Events Carousel:**
```javascript
// Horizontal scroll with smooth behavior
const scrollContainer = useRef(null);

const scrollLeft = () => {
  scrollContainer.current.scrollBy({ left: -300, behavior: 'smooth' });
};

const scrollRight = () => {
  scrollContainer.current.scrollBy({ left: 300, behavior: 'smooth' });
};
```

---

#### 6. Event Detail Page (`07-event-detail.html`)

**Purpose:** Detailed event information and ticket purchase

**Layout Structure:**
1. **Header Section**
   - Back button (top-left)
   - Event cover image (full-width, 400px height)
   - Wishlist button (heart icon, top-right)
   - Share button (top-right)

2. **Event Information Section**
   - Event title (h1)
   - Date and time (icon + text)
   - Venue with map preview (Google Maps embed)
   - Organizer info (avatar, name, rating)
   - Click organizer → Organizer profile (future enhancement)

3. **Description Section**
   - Full event description (markdown/rich text)
   - "Read more" if truncated

4. **Ticket Section**
   - Available ticket types (cards)
   - Each ticket: Name, Price, Description, Quantity available
   - Quantity selector (+ / - buttons)
   - "Buy Tickets" button (sticky on mobile)

5. **Reviews Section**
   - Average rating (stars + number)
   - Total reviews count
   - Individual reviews list
   - Each review: Avatar, Name, Rating, Date, Comment

6. **Actions**
   - Save to wishlist (heart icon)
   - Share event (share icon)

**Implementation Notes:**
```javascript
// Ticket quantity selector
const [tickets, setTickets] = useState({
  'general': 0,
  'vip': 0
});

const updateQuantity = (ticketType, change) => {
  setTickets({
    ...tickets,
    [ticketType]: Math.max(0, tickets[ticketType] + change)
  });
};

// Calculate total
const totalAmount = Object.entries(tickets).reduce((sum, [type, qty]) => {
  return sum + (qty * ticketPrices[type]);
}, 0);

// Buy tickets button
const handleBuyTickets = () => {
  // Validate quantity > 0
  const totalTickets = Object.values(tickets).reduce((a, b) => a + b, 0);
  if (totalTickets === 0) {
    alert('Please select at least one ticket');
    return;
  }
  // Navigate to checkout with selected tickets
  navigate('/checkout', { state: { eventId, tickets } });
};
```

**Wishlist Toggle:**
```javascript
const [isWishlisted, setIsWishlisted] = useState(false);

const toggleWishlist = async () => {
  if (isWishlisted) {
    await removeFromWishlist(eventId);
  } else {
    await addToWishlist(eventId);
  }
  setIsWishlisted(!isWishlisted);
};
```

**Share Functionality:**
```javascript
const handleShare = async () => {
  if (navigator.share) {
    // Web Share API (mobile)
    await navigator.share({
      title: event.title,
      text: event.description,
      url: window.location.href
    });
  } else {
    // Copy to clipboard
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(window.location.href);
    toast.success('Link copied to clipboard');
  }
};
```

---

#### 7. Checkout Page (`08-checkout.html`)

**Purpose:** Payment processing for ticket purchase

**Layout Structure:**
1. **Order Summary Section** (Left/Top)
   - Event name and image
   - Ticket breakdown (type, quantity, unit price, subtotal)
   - Service fee
   - Grand total

2. **Payment Section** (Right/Bottom)
   - Saved payment methods (radio buttons)
   - "Add new card" option
   - Stripe payment form (when new card selected)
   - Billing address
   - "Complete Purchase" button

**Implementation Notes:**
```javascript
// Stripe integration
import { loadStripe } from '@stripe/stripe-js';
import { Elements, CardElement, useStripe, useElements } from '@stripe/react-stripe-js';

const stripePromise = loadStripe('pk_test_...');

const CheckoutForm = () => {
  const stripe = useStripe();
  const elements = useElements();

  const handleSubmit = async (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();

    // Create payment intent on backend
    const { clientSecret } = await createPaymentIntent(totalAmount);

    // Confirm payment
    const result = await stripe.confirmCardPayment(clientSecret, {
      payment_method: {
        card: elements.getElement(CardElement),
        billing_details: { name, email, address }
      }
    });

    if (result.error) {
      setError(result.error.message);
    } else {
      // Payment successful
      navigate('/order-confirmation', { state: { orderId: result.paymentIntent.id } });
    }
  };

  return (
    <form onSubmit={handleSubmit}>
      <CardElement />
      <button type="submit" disabled={!stripe}>Pay ${totalAmount}</button>
    </form>
  );
};
```

**Saved Cards Display:**
```javascript
const [savedCards, setSavedCards] = useState([]);
const [selectedCard, setSelectedCard] = useState(null);

// Load saved cards
useEffect(() => {
  const fetchCards = async () => {
    const cards = await getUserPaymentMethods();
    setSavedCards(cards);
  };
  fetchCards();
}, []);

// Card selection
<div className="space-y-2">
  {savedCards.map(card => (
    <div key={card.id} className="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 border rounded-lg cursor-pointer"
         onClick={() => setSelectedCard(card.id)}>
      <input type="radio" checked={selectedCard === card.id} />
      <span>•••• {card.last4}</span>
      <span>{card.brand}</span>
    </div>
  ))}
</div>
```

