#### 8. Order Confirmation Page (`09-order-confirmation.html`)

**Purpose:** Display purchase success and ticket details

**Layout Structure:**
1. **Success Message**
   - Green checkmark icon
   - "Order Confirmed!" heading
   - Order number

2. **E-Ticket Section**
   - Large QR code (for event check-in)
   - Ticket details (event name, date, venue, tickets)

3. **Event Details Summary**
   - Event image
   - Full details recap

4. **Action Buttons**
   - "Add to Calendar" (download .ics file)
   - "View My Tickets" (navigate to My Tickets page)
   - "Share" button

**Implementation Notes:**
```javascript
// QR Code generation
import QRCode from 'qrcode.react';

<QRCode
  value={ticketId}
  size={256}
  level="H"
  includeMargin={true}
/>

// Add to Calendar (.ics file generation)
const addToCalendar = () => {
  const icsContent = `
BEGIN:VCALENDAR
VERSION:2.0
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:${formatDate(event.startDate)}
DTEND:${formatDate(event.endDate)}
SUMMARY:${event.title}
LOCATION:${event.venue}
DESCRIPTION:${event.description}
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR
  `.trim();

  const blob = new Blob([icsContent], { type: 'text/calendar' });
  const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
  const link = document.createElement('a');
  link.href = url;
  link.download = `${event.title}.ics`;
  link.click();
};
```

