#### 16. Event Creation Page (`18-event-creation.html`)

**Purpose:** Create new event (5-step wizard)

**Layout Structure:**

**Step 1: Basic Info**
- Event title (required)
- Category dropdown (required)
- Description (rich text editor, required)
- Tags (optional)

**Step 2: Date & Location**
- Start date & time (required)
- End date & time (optional)
- Venue name (required)
- Address (required, with autocomplete)
- Map preview (Google Maps)

**Step 3: Media**
- Cover image upload (required, 16:9 aspect ratio)
- Additional photos (optional, up to 10)
- Drag-and-drop zone
- Image preview with crop/edit

**Step 4: Tickets**
- Add ticket types (minimum 1)
- For each ticket type:
  - Name (e.g., "General Admission", "VIP")
  - Price
  - Quantity available
  - Description (optional)
- "Add another ticket type" button

**Step 5: Review & Publish**
- Summary of all entered information
- Edit buttons for each section
- "Save as Draft" button
- "Publish Event" button

**Navigation:**
- Progress indicator (1/5, 2/5, etc.)
- "Back" button (go to previous step)
- "Next" button (go to next step)
- "Save as Draft" (available on all steps)

**Implementation Notes:**
```javascript
const [currentStep, setCurrentStep] = useState(1);
const [formData, setFormData] = useState({
  basicInfo: {},
  dateLocation: {},
  media: {},
  tickets: []
});

// Step validation
const validateStep = (step) => {
  switch(step) {
    case 1:
      return formData.basicInfo.title && formData.basicInfo.category && formData.basicInfo.description;
    case 2:
      return formData.dateLocation.startDate && formData.dateLocation.venue && formData.dateLocation.address;
    case 3:
      return formData.media.coverImage;
    case 4:
      return formData.tickets.length > 0 && formData.tickets.every(t => t.name && t.price >= 0 && t.quantity > 0);
    default:
      return true;
  }
};

const nextStep = () => {
  if (validateStep(currentStep)) {
    setCurrentStep(Math.min(5, currentStep + 1));
  } else {
    alert('Please fill in all required fields');
  }
};

const previousStep = () => {
  setCurrentStep(Math.max(1, currentStep - 1));
};

// Save as draft
const saveAsDraft = async () => {
  await createEvent({ ...formData, status: 'draft' });
  toast.success('Event saved as draft');
  navigate('/organizer/events');
};

// Publish event
const publishEvent = async () => {
  if (!validateStep(4)) {
    alert('Please complete all required information');
    return;
  }

  await createEvent({ ...formData, status: 'published' });
  toast.success('Event published successfully');
  navigate('/organizer/events');
};

// Auto-save (future enhancement)
useEffect(() => {
  const timer = setInterval(() => {
    // Auto-save to localStorage every 30 seconds
    localStorage.setItem('draftEvent', JSON.stringify(formData));
  }, 30000);

  return () => clearInterval(timer);
}, [formData]);
```

