#### 21. Admin User Management (`24-admin-attendees.html`, `25-admin-organizers.html`)

**Purpose:** Manage attendees and organizers

**Layout Structure (Both pages have similar structure):**

1. **Header**
   - Page title ("Attendees" or "Organizers")
   - "Create New" button (opens modal)

2. **Filters & Search Bar**
   - Search input (name, email)
   - Status filter (Active / Suspended / All)
   - Date filter (Joined date range)
   - "Export" button

3. **Data Table**
   - Columns (Attendees):
     - Checkbox (bulk selection)
     - Photo
     - Name
     - Email
     - Join Date
     - Events Attended
     - Status badge
     - Actions (Edit / Suspend / Delete)

   - Columns (Organizers):
     - Checkbox
     - Photo
     - Name
     - Email
     - Join Date
     - Events Created
     - Verification Status
     - Status badge
     - Actions (Edit / Verify / Suspend / Delete)

4. **Pagination**
   - Page numbers
   - Items per page selector (10 / 25 / 50 / 100)

5. **Bulk Actions Bar** (appears when items selected)
   - "X items selected"
   - Bulk actions: Suspend, Delete, Export selected

**Implementation Notes:**
```javascript
// Table with sorting, filtering, pagination
const [users, setUsers] = useState([]);
const [page, setPage] = useState(1);
const [perPage, setPerPage] = useState(25);
const [sortBy, setSortBy] = useState('joinDate');
const [sortOrder, setSortOrder] = useState('desc');
const [filters, setFilters] = useState({ status: 'all', search: '' });

useEffect(() => {
  const fetchUsers = async () => {
    const data = await getUsers({
      type: 'attendee', // or 'organizer'
      page,
      perPage,
      sortBy,
      sortOrder,
      ...filters
    });
    setUsers(data.users);
    setTotalPages(data.totalPages);
  };
  fetchUsers();
}, [page, perPage, sortBy, sortOrder, filters]);

// Bulk selection
const [selectedUsers, setSelectedUsers] = useState([]);

const toggleSelect = (userId) => {
  if (selectedUsers.includes(userId)) {
    setSelectedUsers(selectedUsers.filter(id => id !== userId));
  } else {
    setSelectedUsers([...selectedUsers, userId]);
  }
};

const selectAll = () => {
  setSelectedUsers(users.map(u => u.id));
};

const deselectAll = () => {
  setSelectedUsers([]);
};

// Bulk actions
const bulkSuspend = async () => {
  await suspendUsers(selectedUsers);
  toast.success(`${selectedUsers.length} users suspended`);
  deselectAll();
  // Refresh list
};

// Create user modal
const [showCreateModal, setShowCreateModal] = useState(false);

// Edit user modal
const [editingUser, setEditingUser] = useState(null);

// Suspend user (confirmation)
const suspendUser = async (userId) => {
  if (window.confirm('Are you sure you want to suspend this user?')) {
    await updateUserStatus(userId, 'suspended');
    toast.success('User suspended');
    // Refresh list
  }
};
```

