## Technical Stack

### Frontend

#### Core Technologies
- **Framework**: React 18+ with TypeScript
- **Build Tool**: Vite or Create React App
- **CSS Framework**: Tailwind CSS v3
- **Routing**: React Router v6
- **State Management**: React Context API + useReducer (or Redux Toolkit for complex state)

#### UI Libraries & Utilities
- **Icons**: Iconify (Lucide icon set)
  ```bash
  npm install @iconify/react
  ```
- **Forms**: React Hook Form
  ```bash
  npm install react-hook-form
  ```
- **Validation**: Zod or Yup
  ```bash
  npm install zod
  ```
- **Date Handling**: date-fns or Day.js
  ```bash
  npm install date-fns
  ```
- **QR Codes**: qrcode.react
  ```bash
  npm install qrcode.react
  ```
- **Charts**: Recharts or Chart.js
  ```bash
  npm install recharts
  ```
- **Toast Notifications**: react-hot-toast or react-toastify
  ```bash
  npm install react-hot-toast
  ```
- **Modals**: Headless UI or Radix UI
  ```bash
  npm install @headlessui/react
  ```

#### Payment Integration
- **Stripe**: @stripe/stripe-js + @stripe/react-stripe-js
  ```bash
  npm install @stripe/stripe-js @stripe/react-stripe-js
  ```

#### Authentication
- **Google OAuth**: react-google-login or @react-oauth/google
  ```bash
  npm install @react-oauth/google
  ```

### Backend (NestJS)

#### Core Technologies
- **Framework**: NestJS (Node.js + TypeScript)
- **Database**: PostgreSQL (recommended) or MongoDB
- **ORM**: TypeORM (for PostgreSQL) or Prisma
- **Authentication**: Passport.js + JWT
- **File Upload**: Multer
- **Email**: NodeMailer or SendGrid

#### API Documentation
- **Swagger/OpenAPI**: @nestjs/swagger

### Development Tools

#### Code Quality
- **Linting**: ESLint
- **Formatting**: Prettier
- **Type Checking**: TypeScript strict mode

#### Version Control
- **Git** with conventional commits
- **GitHub** or GitLab

#### Testing (Recommended)
- **Unit Tests**: Jest + React Testing Library
- **E2E Tests**: Playwright or Cypress

